<li><a href="http://www.bopsecrets.org/gateway/passages/baudelaire.htm" class="external text" title="http://www.bopsecrets.org/gateway/passages/baudelaire.htm" rel="nofollow">20 different English translations of Baudelaire's "The Balcony"</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.geocities.com/thedecadents2005/" class="external text" title="http://www.geocities.com/thedecadents2005/" rel="nofollow">La Nouvelle Décadence - Extensive online library of Baudelaire translations and biographies</a></li>
</ul>
